&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Manteno, IL&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department:&lt;/strong&gt; Finance / FP&amp;amp;A&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports To:&lt;/strong&gt; FP&amp;amp;A Director / Head of Finance Transformation&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FLSA Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Exempt&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Gotion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gotion is a global leader in advanced energy storage and battery manufacturing, driving innovation in electrification and clean energy systems. As we scale one of North America’s largest battery production facilities, we are building a next-generation finance organization powered by data, automation, and artificial intelligence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The AI Financial Analyst will support Gotion’s Finance organization by combining traditional FP&amp;amp;A responsibilities with advanced analytics, automation, and AI-driven insights. This role focuses on transforming financial data into predictive insights, building automated reporting systems, and enabling smarter, faster decision-making across manufacturing operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-visibility role ideal for someone who understands finance but is also passionate about AI tools, data science concepts, and modern financial technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Enabled Financial Analysis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop AI-assisted financial models to improve forecasting accuracy and scenario planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use machine learning tools or AI platforms to identify cost trends, anomalies, and operational inefficiencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support predictive analytics for manufacturing costs, labor utilization, and supply chain spend.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex datasets into actionable business insights for leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FP&amp;amp;A &amp;amp; Business Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in budgeting, forecasting, and monthly financial close processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform variance analysis on manufacturing costs, overhead, and operational KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support capital investment analysis and ROI modeling for production expansion projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with operations, engineering, and supply chain teams to understand cost drivers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Automation &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain automated dashboards using Power BI, Tableau, or similar tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Streamline financial reporting processes using Python, SQL, or AI-based tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve data quality, consistency, and accessibility across finance systems.&lt;/li&gt;
