&lt;p&gt;Illinois Manufacturing plant in Manteno, IL. This role will oversee cost accounting, financial planning and analysis, compliance, and internal controls for the site. The Plant Controller will serve as a strategic partner to the Plant Manager and Operations leadership, ensuring financial objectives are aligned with production, quality, and cost efficiency goals. The ideal candidate will bring strong manufacturing finance experience, leadership skills, and the ability to navigate a global, fast-paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
